1
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,680
Kneel here and wait.

2
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,239
Kneeling again?

3
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,599
If I kneel down here,

4
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,040
and the Empress doesn't show up,

5
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,879
won't I be kneeling till I die?

6
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:44,239
But if I break the rules,

7
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,519
they could find any excuse

8
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,480
to charge me with lèse-majesté.

9
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:48,799
Brilliant.

10
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:50,239
Empress,

11
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,920
where are you?

12
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,359
Which way should your subject kneel?

13
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,079
Ning Chen!

14
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,959
No shouting in the Furong Palace.

15
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,319
But I should at least know

16
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,079
which way to kneel toward Her Majesty.

17
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:03,040
It'd be awkward to kneel the wrong way.

18
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,120
Besides,

19
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,719
that would be lèse-majesté.

20
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,200
Just kneel when told.

21
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,319
Enough with the nonsense.

22
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,680
Listen here, sister,

23
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,319
it's not that I don't want to kneel.

24
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:13,919
I just...

25
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,759
I was tortured at the Inspection Bureau.

26
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:18,000
Both my kneecaps are shattered.

27
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:20,439
And my backside is a bloody mess.

28
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,400
It still hurts.

29
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,000
I dare say

30
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,479
the Empress won't strip me to check.

31
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:47,919
So this is the Mother of the Nation?

32
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,360
She looks like a gas tank.

33
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:53,199
How could His Majesty even bear it?

34
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,960
I'm truly impressed.

35
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,599
So you're Ning Chen.

36
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,719
What audacity.

37
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,680
You dare not kneel before Us?

38
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,280
Your subject is wounded.

39
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,560
I cannot bow properly.

40
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,759
Ning Chen,

41
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,639
you rose by trampling the Imperial Uncle.

42
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:15,639
Feeling rather smug, aren't you?

43
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:18,240
The Empress misunderstands.

44
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,159
Your subject killed the Imperial Uncle

45
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,199
out of sheer necessity.

46
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,879
I, your subject,

47
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:26,199
deeply regret it.

48
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:30,159
The Imperial Uncle was Our brother.

49
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,840
You killed him and walked away unscathed.

50
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,919
In all of Daxuan,

51
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,680
no one else compares to you.

52
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:39,120
You should feel smug.

53
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:42,360
Since His Majesty has pardoned you,

54
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,439
We have nothing more to say.

55
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,639
The days ahead are long.

56
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,759
We will remember you well,

57
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,080
Ning Chen.

58
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:57,039
Thank you for your concern, Empress.

59
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,560
Guards!

60
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,840
Ning Chen is unkempt and defies the rules.

61
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,240
This is true lèse-majesté.

62
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,159
Thirty strokes of the cane.

63
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,599
Wait.

64
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,520
We act by protocol. You dare resist?

65
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:09,960
His Majesty ordered me to the border.

66
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,639
Your subject is already wounded.

67
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,560
If punished further,

68
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:16,800
I won't be able to move for a while,

69
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,480
which may delay the war effort.

70
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,519
You dare threaten Us?

71
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,480
If the Empress insists on punishing me,

72
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,800
your subject dares not resist.

73
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,560
Your subject

74
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,600
willingly accepts the punishment.

75
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,319
Delaying war is a state matter.

76
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,079
If His Majesty grows enraged,

77
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:42,439
even We could not bear the blame.

78
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:49,920
Since His Majesty has pardoned you,

79
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,879
today, We shall

80
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,959
spare you for your lèse-majesté.

81
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,240
But you remember this well.

82
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,759
No matter how an ant jumps about,

83
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,800
it remains nothing but an ant.

84
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:03,279
We are the Mother of the Nation.

85
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,000
Crushing an ant

86
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,920
takes no effort at all.

87
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,720
Thank you for your mercy, Empress.

88
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,920
Your subject

89
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,319
will keep this in mind.

90
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,680
Get out!

91
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:22,639
He's infuriating!

92
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,360
Your Majesty,

93
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,560
don't be angry, don't be angry.

94
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,199
He's infuriating!

95
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,079
Chen, Chen.

96
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:47,600
Chen.

97
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,680
What happened?

98
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,839
What's going on?

99
00:05:59,480 --> 00:05:59,959
How did it go?

100
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:00,959
Say something!

101
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,600
His Majesty showed mercy.

102
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,000
He let me see you guys one last time.

103
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,920
I'll be executed in three days.

104
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,480
I'll go see His Majesty.

105
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:28,920
I'll have Geng Ziyi...

106
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,639
His Majesty sent me to the front lines.

107
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,000
To atone for my crimes through merit.

108
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:33,800
So, you see...

109
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,240
I was just messing with you.

110
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,480
What's wrong with you, huh?

111
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,120
Seriously, you little brat.

112
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:41,319
You scared me half to death!

113
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,800
He's crying! He's crying!

114
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,600
I am not.

115
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,800
Still denying it, you little punk?

116
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,160
You almost cried too, Pan Jinyi.

117
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,160
I have no feelings.

118
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,120
What feelings could I have?

119
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,000
No feelings, my foot.

120
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,120
Suddenly you have no feelings again?

121
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:54,839
Alright!

122
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,600
You saved your neck, you little brat.

123
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,040
We've got to celebrate!

124
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,839
Tonight we go to the Jiaofang Si.

125
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,399
My treat.

126
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,680
Sounds great, alright!

127
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:02,959
But...

128
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:05,199
Let me go home and wash up first.

129
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,600
I've been wearing this for days.

130
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:07,279
I stink.

131
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:08,839
Fine.

132
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:09,879
Old Gao.

133
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:11,120
Anyone who heard it is invited.

134
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,399
I'm coming along too.

135
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,480
Hold on.

136
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,600
If they both come, I'm short on cash.

137
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,480
Lend me some first.

138
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,600
Why play the big shot when you're broke?

139
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:21,639
Well...

140
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:22,319
I'll treat then.

141
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,240
Count me in.

142
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,120
I'll tag along too.

143
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,000
Let's all go together.

144
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,000
The Jiaofang Si!

145
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:33,759
Don't yawn.

146
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,839
You're making me yawn too.

147
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,439
Imperial Father.

148
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,199
Greetings, Imperial Father.

149
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,959
Why aren't you in bed at this hour?

150
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,079
Did you come to see me about something?

151
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,560
Imperial Father.

152
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,480
I want to show you something.

153
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,680
What's this?

154
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:48,959
A poem.

155
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:55,680
Clouds long for her gown, blooms her face.

156
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,800
Spring breeze brushes the rail, rich dew.

157
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:04,199
If not seen atop Mount Qunyu,

158
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:08,639
Then met by moonlight on the Jade Terrace.

159
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,759
Beautifully written.

160
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,480
Huai'an.

161
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,120
Huai'an.

162
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,639
This poem...

163
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,920
Did you write it?

164
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,639
Imperial Father!

165
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:29,279
I'm not that shameless.

166
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,680
That rascal Ning Chen gave it to me.

167
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:38,639
So what do you think of Ning Chen?

168
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,600
He's a bit annoying,

169
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,759
but his literary talent is undeniable.

170
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,240
Aside from his talent,

171
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,759
what about his looks?

172
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,519
His looks?

173
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:57,200
Nowhere near as good as yours, Father.

174
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,120
Oh, you.

175
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,159
You really know how to flatter me.

176
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,080
If you admire something about Ning Chen,

177
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,279
that's a good thing.

178
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,000
He gave you a poem.

179
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,759
But what will you give him?

180
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,360
What I'll give him...

181
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,320
I can't think of anything either.

182
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,559
Imperial Father, help me think of a gift.

183
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,240
Give him a shield.

184
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,759
Next time you hit him with a duster,

185
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:26,039
he can block, block, block.

186
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,080
Then you won't scare him away.

187
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,120
Imperial Father!

188
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:32,360
I'm a proper lady, you know.

189
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:33,559
I know.

190
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:36,039
You're my most well-behaved daughter.

191
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:40,919
Does His Majesty want him as a son-in-law?

192
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:41,759
Goodness me.

193
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:45,279
The 9th Princess is his favorite daughter.

194
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,919
A bunch of country bumpkins

195
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,200
coming to the Jiaofang Si?

196
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,720
Who do they think they are?

197
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,000
The people who can come here

198
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:18,080
are mostly rich or noble.

199
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,080
None of them have weak backgrounds.

200
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:21,799
His Majesty lets us indulge ourselves,

201
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,399
but if we cause trouble here,

202
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,679
he won't go easy on us.

203
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:29,159
Boss.

204
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,080
Where is Miss Nanzhi?

205
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,720
Who's Nanzhi?

206
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,559
No wonder they call you a greenhorn,

207
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:36,799
you really don't know a thing.

208
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,600
The Jiaofang Si has twelve chambers,

209
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,200
and each one is filled with beauties.

210
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:42,320
Talented and gorgeous,

211
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,879
they sell their art, not their bodies.

212
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:44,799
Among them,

213
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,799
Miss Nanzhi is the most outstanding.

214
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,919
The flute she plays

215
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,200
is the finest in the capital.

216
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:54,720
No wonder fatty obsesses over this place.

217
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,200
Our boss

218
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,600
has a soft spot for Miss Nanzhi.

219
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,440
He only comes here for her.

220
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,840
The mighty Pan Jinyi of the Bureau

221
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:05,240
can't even win over a courtesan?

222
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,000
In this capital city,

223
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,200
the men wanting to take Miss Nanzhi

224
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,519
are too many to count.

225
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,639
Our boss earns plenty,

226
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,679
but compared to those

227
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,639
truly wealthy and powerful men,

228
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,440
he falls short.

229
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,879
And our boss,

230
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,840
he's just not good with words.

231
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,120
Every time, he can only watch from afar.

232
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:28,360
Young Master Gao.

233
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,840
Madam San.

234
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:32,200
Come, come.

235
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,559
Find a fine seat for us young masters.

236
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,639
Right away, Young Master Gao.

237
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:38,759
Your private booth

238
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,559
has been ready for a while.

239
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:41,320
Let's go.

240
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:43,840
Young Master Ning, after you.

241
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,759
Ladies, come quickly!

242
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,399
Still so lively in here.

243
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:48,759
Young Master Ning, take the head seat.

244
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,440
Where are our girls?

245
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,720
Don't be impatient.

246
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,480
Come.

247
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,639
Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter.

248
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,080
Do you like them?

249
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,679
Serve the young masters well.

250
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,840
We greet you, young masters.

251
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:05,679
Don't be shy.

252
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:07,440
Come on, Chen.

253
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:08,519
You pick first.

254
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,080
Hold on.

255
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:09,679
I...

256
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,120
You four ladies

257
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,720
should go attend to your own matters.

258
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:15,759
What?

259
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:16,440
Winter, Autumn.

260
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,720
What are you doing, sending them away?

261
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,519
Think about it.

262
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,399
With Ning Chen's current status,

263
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:23,639
are these ordinary girls really worthy?

264
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:26,080
He deserves a girl from the 12 Chambers.

265
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,000
That makes sense.

266
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,360
Ning Chen,

267
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,840
your taste has gotten higher.

268
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:33,600
How about a different selection?

269
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,360
No, no, no need.

270
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,000
You all enjoy yourselves.

271
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:35,960
I'll just watch.

272
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,200
Don't hold back here.

273
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,120
A first-timer.

274
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,200
So bashful.

275
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,600
But what he said makes sense.

276
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:49,200
The girl who serves you tonight

277
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,639
should pay you instead.

278
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,879
This is your first time.

279
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,200
The highest bidder wins.

280
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,000
Let me arrange it.

281
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,320
Everyone!

282
00:12:58,919 --> 00:12:59,759
Everyone!

283
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:02,559
Hear me out for a moment.

284
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:05,720
Especially the girls of the 12 Chambers.

285
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,879
We have here one...

286
00:13:07,919 --> 00:13:08,559
Get the hell out of here.

287
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:09,559
My buddy here had too much to drink.

288
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,120
It's fine.

289
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:12,840
You shut your mouth.

290
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,360
Quietly wait for your Twelve Chambers.

291
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:17,080
Still being shy.

292
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,600
Young masters,

293
00:13:20,879 --> 00:13:23,840
Lady Nanzhi and Lady Yudie will perform.

294
00:13:24,159 --> 00:13:27,200
Each table gets a pot of wine

295
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:29,480
and two side dishes.

296
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:32,679
Great, great, great.

297
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:34,440
Dim the lights.

298
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,919
Ning, you really lucked out today.

299
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,399
Lady Nanzhi's flute

300
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:47,679
and Lady Yudie's pipa

301
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:50,039
are the two finest in the capital.

302
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,840
Relax.

